creator: Ethics Infotech LLP
descriptionHtml:
We are India's leading & most-trusted fastest growing private owned generic pharmacy chain. From sear of generic medicine franchise request, its location and approval to execution of store and opening schedule this user can get all details in single application.


At davaindia generic pharmacy store execution app you can:

- location request for new franchisee store.

- payment details.

- document submission.

- process tracking.

- chat communication.


Permissions Explained:

- Identity: To help make the sign-up & login process smoother

- SMS: To support automatic OTP confirmation, so that you don't have to enter the authentication code.

- location: To know your store location for approval process.

- Camera: to get document and store picture for store execution process
